text: Cees Benedictus-Lieftinck (16 June 1920 - 25 February 2008) was a Dutch equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Dutch female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Groningen (city)
